HEADWORD: Rotella
<hw>Ro*tel"la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., dim. of
<ets>rota</ets> wheel; cf. LL. <ets>rotella</ets> a little whell.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of numerous species of small, polished,
brightcolored gastropods of the genus <gen>Rotella</gen>, native of
tropical seas.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

